    "name": "A Tiny Sticker Tale",
    "steam_appid": 2322180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/b3de57367aa7a599f370b5ea1f43b1ec.avif?t=1754937906\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《小贴纸故事》是一场关于利用贴纸的力量改变世界的舒适微型冒险！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*(这是一次感性而短暂的体验，主要故事大约需要 2 小时。)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/e225f8f7086426ac498f09e44b883e8d.poster.avif?t=1754937906\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/e225f8f7086426ac498f09e44b883e8d.webm?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/e225f8f7086426ac498f09e44b883e8d.mp4?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>在《小贴纸故事》，从你周围的世界中获取任何东西，将其变成贴纸，然后利用你的创造力将其贴回不同的地方，解决谜题并帮助你的新朋友！</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/45f0c36fb857464084dd815fb95be4b4.avif?t=1754937906\" width=600 height=215 /></span>在这个健康的小冒险中，穿上驴子弗林的小靴子，穿越菲戈里岛，发现充满活力的任务，这需要一本非常特殊的魔法贴纸书的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/3ac095eab8f8ea2af0011bc23d0e7e1f.poster.avif?t=1754937906\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/3ac095eab8f8ea2af0011bc23d0e7e1f.webm?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/3ac095eab8f8ea2af0011bc23d0e7e1f.mp4?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的游戏玩法，发挥你的创造力，通过在不同的地方放置贴纸来解决谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过放置贴纸来改变你的周围环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照您想要的方式定制和装饰您的岛屿！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >菲戈里岛有着华丽、迷人的艺术风格，是一整天冒险后休息的完美场所</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满神秘和冒险的细致而迷人的岛屿</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集岛上的所有贴纸</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/18924d364c57b02495d225f214083659.poster.avif?t=1754937906\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/18924d364c57b02495d225f214083659.webm?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322180/extras/18924d364c57b02495d225f214083659.mp4?t=1754937906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*<strong>《小贴纸故事》被设计为一个短篇冒险，充满了许多细节、主要故事的精彩附加内容以及大量的可重玩性！</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ogre Pixel </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2023</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
